snippet.title: Kill Shot 1506 meters - Sniper Ghost Warrior Contracts 2 Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
Shots have never been made from such long distances before. Sniper Ghost Warrior Contracts 2 introduces fans to a dramatic single-player campaign where the stakes are at their highest, deep inside enemy territory.
For the first time, Sniper Ghost Warrior Contracts 2 delivers precision long-range shooting campaign with targets over 1,000 meters away.
